00:21:17.446 --> 00:21:19.276
So let's see what we need to do

00:21:19.276 --> 00:21:21.746
to add iAd Support
to this application.

00:21:22.206 --> 00:21:23.986
We're going to hide
this, go back,

00:21:23.986 --> 00:21:26.206
to Xcode to bring
